VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'going to be live with Julia McCoy. We\'re going to talk about creating a digital twin that people actually trust. So, we\'re so glad you could join us. I\'m Audrey. I\'m the community manager here at HeyGen. I\'ll be your host for'

[00:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'today\'s webinar. I\'m calling in from San Francisco, California. And before we get into it, a little housekeeping. If you do have any questions for our speaker, please go'

